OL,3,CConclave: How is a new Pope elected?
OL,5,FCardinals are senior members of the
OL,6,Fclergy, many who are bishops and
OL,7,Farchbishops appointed by the pope.
OL,9,FThe rules of the conclave, as of
OL,10,FJanuary 22, 2025, stated there are 138
OL,11,Felectors - and therefore 138 eligible
OL,12,Fpapal candidates - of the 252
OL,13,Fcardinals.
OL,15,FOnly those under the age of 80 may
OL,16,Ftake part in the secret ballot.
OL,18,FHow does the vote take place?
