OL,3,CConclave: How is a new Pope elected?
OL,5,FOnce the cardinals have arrived, the
OL,6,Fconclave begins with a special morning
OL,7,FMass in St Peter's Basilica. In the
OL,8,Fafternoon, the cardinals walk to the
OL,9,FSistine Chapel to start the voting
OL,10,Fprocess.
OL,12,FThe College of Cardinals then take a
OL,13,Fvow of secrecy inside the chapel and,
OL,14,Fwith the exception of a few workers,
OL,15,Fno one else is allowed in.
OL,17,FAll communications with the outside
OL,18,Fworld, including phones and the
OL,19,Finternet, are removed and the chapel
OL,20,Fis checked for recording devices.
