OL,3,CConclave: How is a new Pope elected?
OL,5,FIf the first ballot does not produce a
OL,6,Fresult, a maximum of four ballots are
OL,7,Fheld on each successive day: two in
OL,8,Feach morning and two in each afternoon.
OL,10,FThe process is repeated for three
OL,11,Fdays, after which there is a day's
OL,12,Frest for prayer, reflection and
OL,13,Finformal discussions.
OL,15,FThe voting then begins again for a
OL,16,Fseries of seven more ballots and then
OL,17,Fanother break.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
